    <item>
      <title>廉价药物可能会延缓衰老。一项研究将确定它是否有效</title>
      <link>https://npr.org/sections/health-shots/2024/04/22/1245872510/a-cheap-drug-may-slow-down-aging-a-study-will-determine-if-it-works</link>
      <description><![CDATA[研究表明，服用二甲双胍治疗糖尿病的人患癌症、心脏病和痴呆的风险可能较低。现在研究人员的目标是测试它是否可以预防健康人的与年龄相关的疾病。]]></description>
      <guid>https://npr.org/sections/health-shots/2024/04/22/1245872510/a-cheap-drug-may-slow-down-aging-a-study-will-determine-if-it-works</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 09:01:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院考虑城市是否可以惩罚露宿在外的无家可归者</title>
      <link>https://npr.org/2024/04/22/1245575331/supreme-court-weighs-whether-cities-can-punish-unhoused-people-for-sleeping-outs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[下级法院裁定，如果没有可用的庇护所，在公共土地上罚款或监禁人们是“残酷和不寻常的”。俄勒冈州的一座城市表示，这阻碍了确保公共空间安全并向所有人开放的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://npr.org/2024/04/22/1245575331/supreme-court-weighs-whether-cities-can-punish-unhoused-people-for-sleeping-outs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 09:00:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
